### INSTALL
$ git clone https://github.com/klik-on/nc.git
$ cd nc
$ docker compose up -d
 Network nc_default     Created 
 Volume "nc_db"         Created        
 Volume "nc_nextcloud"  Created
 Container nc-db-1      Started
 Container nc-app-1     Started
